676
01:06:25,417 --> 01:06:26,833
We did everything we could.

677
01:06:27,000 --> 01:06:28,000
Take care.

678
01:07:25,000 --> 01:07:27,083
This watch didn't work anymore.

679
01:07:29,667 --> 01:07:32,708
It costs a lot for maintenance so he didn't.

680
01:07:36,042 --> 01:07:38,583
He said it's not about knowing the time.

681
01:07:39,792 --> 01:07:41,750
It's about showing off.

682
01:07:46,792 --> 01:07:48,542
I know he loved me very much.

683
01:07:49,625 --> 01:07:51,583
He just never said it.

684
01:07:56,625 --> 01:07:59,208
The cheesecake that I like is very expensive.

685
01:08:00,500 --> 01:08:02,375
He bought it on two occasions.

686
01:08:04,792 --> 01:08:06,958
The first time is after my mum left us.

687
01:08:10,083 --> 01:08:12,582
He held the cake telling me that

688
01:08:12,583 --> 01:08:14,625
my mum would never come back.

689
01:08:17,125 --> 01:08:19,875
The second time is after we
met with the Headmaster.

690
01:08:21,125 --> 01:08:22,750
He didn't blame me at all.

691
01:08:27,458 --> 01:08:29,375
I don't understand why.

692
01:08:30,583 --> 01:08:34,292
I can only taste my favourite food
when I am the most upset.

693
01:08:40,875 --> 01:08:42,333
Right now.

694
01:08:45,958 --> 01:08:47,917
I can taste it again.

695
01:09:02,875 --> 01:09:05,292
The moment I know something happened to my dad.

696
01:09:05,708 --> 01:09:07,542
I don't know why I called you right away.

697
01:09:10,500 --> 01:09:13,250
Don't worry. I'm fine.

698
01:09:16,500 --> 01:09:17,874
Where's your boyfriend?

699
01:09:17,875 --> 01:09:19,333
Is anyone walking you home?

700
01:09:24,083 --> 01:09:25,458
