701
01:09:47,375 --> 01:09:49,417
Who is the family representative?

702
01:10:30,708 --> 01:10:32,041
Sylvia.

703
01:10:32,042 --> 01:10:33,999
Come to the U.S. with me.

704
01:10:34,000 --> 01:10:35,208
I'll take care of you all.

705
01:10:36,042 --> 01:10:37,542
I promised my dad

706
01:10:38,542 --> 01:10:40,083
