707
01:10:40,875 --> 01:10:42,457
You're just a student.

708
01:10:42,458 --> 01:10:44,208
How are you supposed to take care of them?

709
01:10:46,292 --> 01:10:49,000
We didn't need your care before.

710
01:10:50,375 --> 01:10:51,792
We certainly don't need it now.

711
01:10:59,833 --> 01:11:00,958
Sylvia.

712
01:11:02,625 --> 01:11:03,958
I'm your mother.

713
01:11:05,542 --> 01:11:08,292
Stop treating me like a stranger.

714
01:11:11,583 --> 01:11:13,375
If you are my family

715
01:11:14,125 --> 01:11:15,833
you could be joining us just then.

716
01:11:32,333 --> 01:11:34,042
I'll make you two some food.

717
01:11:34,708 --> 01:11:38,292
It's fine. We'll go grab a bite.

718
01:11:41,292 --> 01:11:43,208
I'm not hungry. You two go ahead.

719
01:11:46,000 --> 01:11:47,416
Be careful.

720
01:11:47,417 --> 01:11:48,375
Got it.

721
01:11:50,583 --> 01:11:51,833
Let me help.

722
01:11:59,625 --> 01:12:01,042
I'll take a shower first.

723
01:12:31,417 --> 01:12:32,833
You don't need to pretend to be strong.

724
01:12:44,875 --> 01:12:48,292
I'm scared.

725
01:12:48,958 --> 01:12:51,417
Don't be. I'm here.

726
01:12:53,250 --> 01:12:54,457
I know you need me.

727
01:12:54,458 --> 01:12:56,125
Can we start again?

728
01:12:57,250 --> 01:12:59,042
As long as we're together,
everything will be fine.

729
01:13:53,708 --> 01:13:56,125
By the time we reach 30

730
01:13:58,417 --> 01:14:00,708
if we are both still single.

731
01:14:04,083 --> 01:14:05,958
We will get married.

732
01:14:08,167 --> 01:14:09,750
During this time

733
01:14:10,625 --> 01:14:13,333
let's not see each other anymore.

734
01:14:17,333 --> 01:14:18,583
Okay.

735
01:14:20,417 --> 01:14:22,000
It's a deal.

736
01:14:58,292 --> 01:14:59,750
After that night,

737
01:15:00,375 --> 01:15:01,958
I didn't contact her.

738
01:15:03,042 --> 01:15:07,208
When I finally had the guts to open her ICQ,

739
01:15:07,958 --> 01:15:09,625
I found out she quitted school.

740
01:15:10,250 --> 01:15:11,625
She found a job.

741
01:15:13,667 --> 01:15:17,167
Wing, why did you change your Major to Film?

742
01:15:17,292 --> 01:15:19,292
I know a girl.

743
01:15:19,625 --> 01:15:21,375
Movie was everything she dreamt of.

744
01:15:22,125 --> 01:15:24,250
But she has to give it up for some reasons.

745
01:15:24,708 --> 01:15:26,458
I am hoping to make her dream come true.

746
01:15:30,542 --> 01:15:33,667
If it is good, I'd only watch it halfway.

747
01:15:34,208 --> 01:15:37,042
I'd thought of an ending
before I go watch it again.

748
01:15:37,458 --> 01:15:40,500
To compare my ideas with the director's.

749
01:15:42,167 --> 01:15:43,374
Five seconds.

750
01:15:43,375 --> 01:15:44,333
Three.

751
01:15:56,417 --> 01:15:58,250
I was desperate to truly grow up.

752
01:15:59,042 --> 01:16:02,083
That's why I moved out soon after graduation.

753
01:16:02,958 --> 01:16:05,500
I want to live on my own.

754
01:16:08,125 --> 01:16:09,457
I remember when I was a student,

755
01:16:09,458 --> 01:16:11,833
I dreamt of getting a job and being an adult.

756
01:16:12,333 --> 01:16:14,375
But when you're out wandering in the real world,

757
01:16:16,417 --> 01:16:18,250
You always wish to go back to being a student.

758
01:16:21,333 --> 01:16:22,457
Some may say,

759
01:16:22,458 --> 01:16:24,833
Hard work is a form of laziness.

760
01:16:26,208 --> 01:16:27,832
When I reached 24,

761
01:16:27,833 --> 01:16:30,000
Life is nothing but a blur.

762
01:16:31,042 --> 01:16:33,416
The most powerful side effect of working

763
01:16:33,417 --> 01:16:36,000
in the film industry is it wipes out
your concept of time.

764
01:16:38,333 --> 01:16:40,332
I cannot recall the number.

765
01:16:40,333 --> 01:16:41,707
Of movies I've participated in;

766
01:16:41,708 --> 01:16:43,583
Or the places I've flew to.

767
01:16:44,708 --> 01:16:46,750
Until one day, I walked pass her home

768
01:16:47,708 --> 01:16:49,250
while location scouting.

769
01:16:51,542 --> 01:16:53,124
All of a sudden,

770
01:16:53,125 --> 01:16:55,124
I was afraid, that I will be too numb

771
01:16:55,125 --> 01:16:56,750
to feel anything anymore.

772
01:17:06,083 --> 01:17:07,125
Hello?

773
01:17:08,542 --> 01:17:09,583
Hello?

774
01:17:10,542 --> 01:17:11,750
