789
01:18:53,667 --> 01:18:54,667
Thanks.

790
01:19:13,542 --> 01:19:14,542
Are you shy?

791
01:19:17,500 --> 01:19:18,875
Not when I'm with you.

792
01:19:24,083 --> 01:19:25,458
It's as if you never grew up.

793
01:19:25,917 --> 01:19:26,875
You are almost 30.

794
01:19:26,876 --> 01:19:28,583
Why are you still wearing a bra like that?

795
01:19:29,542 --> 01:19:30,292
Yeah.

796
01:19:30,833 --> 01:19:32,625
