809
01:20:32,042 --> 01:20:34,167
Keep spinning... That's right.

810
01:20:34,542 --> 01:20:35,625
Hi, Ms Lee.

811
01:20:35,917 --> 01:20:37,749
Can you share with us.

812
01:20:37,750 --> 01:20:40,333
What kind of story your film tells?

813
01:20:43,500 --> 01:20:47,042
The same event, from two perspectives,

814
01:20:47,792 --> 01:20:50,375
