815
01:20:51,000 --> 01:20:52,792
My film is about a girl

816
01:20:53,167 --> 01:20:56,667
searching for another girl,

817
01:20:57,917 --> 01:21:00,750
To see if what they have gone through

818
01:21:01,542 --> 01:21:03,125
during their high school years

819
01:21:04,917 --> 01:21:07,458
has turned into the same memory.

820
01:22:40,042 --> 01:22:41,208
Why are you laughing?

821
01:22:42,875 --> 01:22:44,458
You got it wrong again.

822
01:23:02,375 --> 01:23:03,958
Remember this ring?

823
01:23:07,125 --> 01:23:09,375
Turns out it's in the
school locker all these time.

824
01:23:13,833 --> 01:23:15,667
I used to like this ring before.

825
01:23:18,708 --> 01:23:20,042
Sylvia,

826
01:23:22,583 --> 01:23:26,083
You will belong to someone else
the moment you walk out.

827
01:23:28,917 --> 01:23:30,625
Can I ask you a question?

828
01:23:31,375 --> 01:23:32,416
Fine.

829
01:23:32,417 --> 01:23:33,625
Go ahead.

830
01:23:40,917 --> 01:23:43,374
What happened to us in high school.

831
01:23:43,375 --> 01:23:45,208
Is that love?

832
01:23:48,792 --> 01:23:51,332
The ceremony will begin in <i>5</i> minutes,
please be ready.

833
01:23:51,333 --> 01:23:52,917
It's time to go.

834
01:24:57,042 --> 01:24:58,333
Sylvia,

835
01:24:59,417 --> 01:25:00,042
promise me,

836
01:25:00,043 --> 01:25:01,250
