838
01:25:13,208 --> 01:25:14,875
Why did you say yes?

839
01:25:18,583 --> 01:25:20,833
Because I don't want to lose a friend.

840
01:25:23,208 --> 01:25:24,875
Because.

841
01:25:25,542 --> 01:25:27,417
You are my only friend.

842
01:25:37,917 --> 01:25:42,666
<i>Looking back to our days on campus.</i>

843
01:25:42,667 --> 01:25:49,332
<i>Your every smile messes up my mind.</i>

844
01:25:49,333 --> 01:25:56,667
<i>Dancing in the hall together,
we never felt tired.</i>

845
01:25:57,167 --> 01:26:01,916
<i>The smell of our classroom,
mixed with summer rain.</i>

846
01:26:01,917 --> 01:26:04,332
<i>How reckless were we.</i>

847
01:26:04,333 --> 01:26:11,624
<i>To cut through all the red tapes.</i>

848
01:26:11,625 --> 01:26:16,500
<i>Who chose to stay put?</i>

849
01:26:17,542 --> 01:26:23,249
<i>Started out as confidantes</i>

850
01:26:23,250 --> 01:26:27,041
<i>even though we were both curious.</i>

851
01:26:27,042 --> 01:26:29,250
<i>Do you still remember?</i>

852
01:26:29,542 --> 01:26:35,208
<i>How we long for, yet to afraid to touch.</i>

853
01:26:36,542 --> 01:26:42,624
<i>The spark was so bright.</i>

854
01:26:42,625 --> 01:26:46,249
<i>Concealing the bittersweet goodbye</i>

855
01:26:46,250 --> 01:26:55,958
<i>I was all alone to carry on the last act.</i>

856
01:27:13,708 --> 01:27:14,958
They're waiting for you.

857
01:27:20,875 --> 01:27:22,792
Don't cry. It messes up your makeup.

858
01:27:31,625 --> 01:27:32,874
Mr. Chung-wai Yau.

859
01:27:32,875 --> 01:27:36,833
Do you take Ms. Sylvia Lee
as your lawful wife?

860
01:27:37,208 --> 01:27:38,292
I do.

861
01:27:39,042 --> 01:27:40,374
Ms. Sylvia Lee,

862
01:27:40,375 --> 01:27:44,791
Do you take Mr. Chung-wai Yau
as your lawful husband?

863
01:27:44,792 --> 01:27:49,000
In sickness and in health, to love and cherish...

864
01:27:49,250 --> 01:27:55,166
<i>Started out as confidantes.</i>

865
01:27:55,167 --> 01:27:59,708
It's totally normal to be confused.

866
01:28:00,833 --> 01:28:02,542
It's just an illusion.

867
01:28:03,292 --> 01:28:04,832
Once we grow up,

868
01:28:04,833 --> 01:28:10,000
we will realise how childish we are being now.

869
01:28:10,167 --> 01:28:13,749
<i>The spark was so bright.</i>

870
01:28:13,750 --> 01:28:17,249
<i>Only to prepare for our goodbye.</i>

871
01:28:17,250 --> 01:28:24,249
<i>I'm left alone, with no regrets.</i>

872
01:28:24,250 --> 01:28:25,917
I do.

873
01:28:26,500 --> 01:28:32,208
<i>Standing by your side as a confidante,</i>

874
01:28:33,375 --> 01:28:35,458
I love you.

875
01:28:38,333 --> 01:28:39,667
I do.

876
01:28:44,542 --> 01:28:50,082
<i>The day has finally come,
I cannot turn back time,</i>

877
01:28:50,083 --> 01:28:53,374
<i>Cannot run from my feelings.</i>

878
01:28:53,375 --> 01:28:56,666
<i>All I could do, is to be with you.</i>

879
01:28:56,667 --> 01:29:02,375
<i>My Dear, My Best friend.</i>

880
01:29:23,625 --> 01:29:27,125
Everything has to come to an end someday.

881
01:29:28,167 --> 01:29:31,958
Just like there's an ending to every movie.

882
01:29:32,917 --> 01:29:36,250
We don't always get to bid farewell.

883
01:29:37,125 --> 01:29:40,832
We spend our six years of primary school,

884
01:29:40,833 --> 01:29:42,667
To long for the seven years of secondary school.

885
01:29:43,708 --> 01:29:45,958
Then we spend our seven years of secondary school,

886
01:29:46,625 --> 01:29:48,292
To long for the three years of university.

887
01:29:49,250 --> 01:29:51,541
At the end we spend the rest of our lives,

888
01:29:51,542 --> 01:29:53,792
to reminisce about our youth.

889
01:29:55,500 --> 01:29:57,750
I wonder how many people are like us,

890
01:29:58,458 --> 01:30:01,583
dare to like yet too frightened to love?

891
01:30:04,708 --> 01:30:08,583
Hey, it's our last scene together.

892
01:30:10,125 --> 01:30:12,457
I just realise.

893
01:30:12,458 --> 01:30:14,958
That I'm the supporting role in your life movie.

894
01:30:17,167 --> 01:30:18,667
For some reasons

895
01:30:19,750 --> 01:30:23,541
all I could recall at this very moment

896
01:30:23,542 --> 01:30:25,792
is what you said to me on that fateful day.

897
01:30:28,167 --> 01:30:29,792
You were right.

898
01:30:31,333 --> 01:30:33,832
Whatever happens in the future.

899
01:30:33,833 --> 01:30:36,917
Perhaps I'll leave Hong Kong for good;

900
01:30:37,750 --> 01:30:39,458
Perhaps you'll become a mother;

901
01:30:40,958 --> 01:30:44,042
Or perhaps I'll find another Sylvia Lee.

902
01:30:47,500 --> 01:30:49,083
We

903
01:30:50,667 --> 01:30:52,000
Will always

904
01:30:52,917 --> 01:30:56,417
always be best friends

905
01:31:00,125 --> 01:31:02,208
forever.

906
01:31:15,083 --> 01:31:17,958
I never regretted liking that girl.

907
01:31:18,542 --> 01:31:20,374
It must have been love.

908
01:31:20,375 --> 01:31:25,458
Your significant other doesn't have to be male,

909
01:31:25,542 --> 01:31:29,416
We should look for spiritual connection.

910
01:31:29,417 --> 01:31:32,624
A lot of girls study in single-sex schools

911
01:31:32,625 --> 01:31:37,041
I believe some have developed

912
01:31:37,042 --> 01:31:38,624
profound relationships in school.

913
01:31:38,625 --> 01:31:41,624
Which is hard to come by.

914
01:31:41,625 --> 01:31:44,749
Even though you didn't end up with that person,

915
01:31:44,750 --> 01:31:48,291
It doesn't mean the memories
you shared aren't real

916
01:31:48,292 --> 01:31:50,457
I know we aren't meant to be together forever,

917
01:31:50,458 --> 01:31:53,999
I hope you can find your passion

918
01:31:54,000 --> 01:31:56,624
and live happily ever after.

919
01:31:56,625 --> 01:31:59,417
Never stop pursuing happiness.

920
01:31:59,958 --> 01:32:03,124
No matter what happens in life,

921
01:32:03,125 --> 01:32:09,041
The intimacy we share won't fade,

922
01:32:09,042 --> 01:32:11,875
you will always hold a special place in my heart.

923
01:32:12,250 --> 01:32:13,083
Although there's regret,

924
01:32:13,084 --> 01:32:17,583
I still wish her all the happiness in life.
